{"tid":2361463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！！江湖救急","createTime":"2021-01-10T16:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T10:32:26.000Z","uid":370462,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"492590116b75d5d0b4b8404c8c6b7624db598a57","tid":2361463,"uid":370462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"東華三院辛亥年總理中學上星期五臨時發網上通告，要求中四中五下星期（即明天起）必須回校補課。<br />\n<br />\n隨即有同學發現有部分日子違反教育局規定的1/6人（如20/1，3/2，4/2等等）。同學因疫情和違反規定的各種原因，於Sun Hoi Secret 討論並發起聯署希望撤回補課安排。但新上任的李校長漠視同學的要求和安危，再出通告拒絕同學所有訴求。更有部份班別的老師指出不容許同學缺席補課，否則測驗等等以零分計算。<br />\n<br />\n明天已有同學自發行動14:45開始罷課，要求校長回應及撤回補課，希望各位幫手spread 出去。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">救救辛亥學生，我哋唔想中武肺。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSLGJfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSLGJfO.png&h=c3c01aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceu0YPf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fceu0YPf.png&h=7e178749&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2374a7697d5dc5a651548036c778e8055a58751e","tid":2361463,"uid":235796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb696a52b2846d5f851714e71b410b66f7ede11","tid":2361463,"uid":370462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"push 推呀"},{"pid":"ac54e3612a167f374ff0842ed1ca83249b452e03","tid":2361463,"uid":370462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"求各位幫推！"},{"pid":"c8a77ae4b979eda7b144e27db84979517ee2b6d6","tid":2361463,"uid":370462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T16:23:18.000Z","msg":